59 (C) No report shall be filed unless the same has been approved prior to the date of
60 abolishment specified in this resolution by majority vote of a quorum of the committee.
61 A report so approved shall be signed by the chairperson of the committee and filed with
62 the Secretary of the Senate.
63 (D) In the absence of an approved report, the chairperson may file with the Secretary
64 of the Senate a copy of the minutes of the meetings of the committee in lieu thereof.
65 (7) Abolishment. The committee shall stand abolished on December 1, 2025.
